    {
      "id": "p007",
      "index": 7,
      "source": "For rack-to-rack interconnect, we explore two different topologies. The first is a two-layer CLOS network that is similar to the Oberon form factor, but with twice the bandwidth of each GPU and NVLink switch.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
